title: You'll Never Believe What Happened When Moe Ran Into This Actress
description:
Moe recently shared the good news of his sons being featured on the BET show "Tales." It was a HUGE win for him and a very exciting moment. So you can imagine how he felt when he ran into one of the stars of the show in the same week.
Moe expected the encounter to go well, but something odd happened instead.
